tp:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce0c814b98\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ayesha-siddiqui\/#WikiBiography\" title=\"Wiki\/Biography\">Wiki\/Biography<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ayesha-siddiqui\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ayesha-siddiqui\/#Family\" title=\"Family\">Family<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ayesha-siddiqui\/#Parents_Siblings\" title=\"Parents &amp; Siblings\">Parents &amp; Siblings<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/ayesha-siddiqui\/#Wife_Children\" title=\"Wife &amp; Children\">Wife &amp; Children<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span>Wiki\/Biography<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ayesha Siddiqui was born as Maha Siddiqui <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_233317_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_233317_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/reviewit.pk\/timeline-of-shoaib-maliks-marriages\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Review It<\/a><\/span><\/span> in Banjara Hills, Hyderabad, India.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span>Physical Appearance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour:<\/strong> Brown<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour:<\/strong> Brown<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span>Family<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>She belongs to a Muslim family.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Parents_Siblings\"><\/span><strong>Parents &amp; Siblings<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Her father\u2019s name is M A Siddiqui, and her mother\u2019s name is Farisa Siddiqui.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_233321\" style=\"width: 390px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddiques-father.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-233321\" class=\"size-full wp-image-233321\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddiques-father.jpg\" alt=\"Ayesha Siddique's father\" width=\"380\" height=\"324\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddiques-father.jpg 380w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddiques-father-300x256.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 380px) 100vw, 380px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-233321\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ayesha Siddique&#8217;s father<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_233322\" style=\"width: 262px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddiques-mother.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-233322\" class=\" wp-image-233322\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddiques-mother.jpg\" alt=\"Ayesha Siddique's mother\" width=\"252\" height=\"379\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddiques-mother.jpg 205w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddiques-mother-200x300.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 252px) 100vw, 252px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-233322\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ayesha Siddique&#8217;s mother<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Wife_Children\"><\/span><strong>Wife &amp; Children<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>On 3 June 2002, she got married to the Pakistani cricketer <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/shoaib-malik\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Shoaib Malik<\/a>, but their wedding remained a secret until Malik got married to the Indian tennis player <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sania-mirza\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Sania Mirza<\/a> in 2010. Initially, Shoaib denied his marriage to Ayesha. However, later, he shared that Ayesha had committed fraud with him. In an interview, he shared that in 2001, while he was in Sharjah to play a cricket match for the Pakistani cricket team, Ayesha called her and introduced her as a fan of Shoaib. They exchanged their phone numbers and regularly started talking to each other. He said that Ayesha sent him photographs of her. Shoaib showed those photos to his parents as well.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_233319\" style=\"width: 377px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddique-with-Shoaib-Malik.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-233319\" class=\" wp-image-233319\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddique-with-Shoaib-Malik.jpg\" alt=\"Ayesha Siddique with Shoaib Malik\" width=\"367\" height=\"263\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddique-with-Shoaib-Malik.jpg 500w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Ayesha-Siddique-with-Shoaib-Malik-300x215.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 367px) 100vw, 367px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-233319\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ayesha Siddique with Shoaib Malik<\/p><\/div>\n<p>He then asked Ayesha to meet his parents, but she kept on resisting. Malik said that she said they would meet at their wedding only. According to some reports, Ayesha once met him with one of her cousins and introduced her cousin as Ayesha. In an interview, Shoaib shared that when he met Ayesha with her parents, he was in shock as the real Ayesha was completely different from her photos, and she had sent some other girls&#8217; photos claiming them as her photos. According to Ayesha\u2019s father, Ayesha and Shoaib had a nikah over a phone call in June 2002. In an interview, Malik said,<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>I was just 20 then, and under a lot of pressure from Ayesha to get married as she was saying that her family was losing face in Hyderabad as word had got around that we were courting. I walked out of my house one morning in June 2002 and went to my friend&#8217;s shop and called from there. I got a nikahnama, signed it, thinking the girl I was marrying was the one in the photographs.\u201d<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>In 2010, when Shoaib announced his marriage to Sania, Ayesha and her parents came out in the media and asked Shoaib to divorce his first wife Ayesha. On 7 April 2010, Malik divorced Ayesha and paid Rs 15 crore as an alimony.<\/p>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_label_expand_233317_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">References<\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_plus_233317_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[+]<\/span><span><\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_minus_233317_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button collapsed\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_233317_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[\u2212]<\/span><\/p><\/div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container_233317_1\" class=\"collapsed\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">References<\/caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_233317_1_1\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>1<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugi